included.description:
I provide health and fitness consumer insights for the Microsoft Band (wearable fitness device) and Health smartphone application. Experienced in hardware and software research, including planning, execution, analysis, and delivery of findings to stakeholders. Presented key insights directly to Senior Design, Marketing, Project Managers, and Engineers. Areas of focus include market research, human factors, interviews, usability, competitor benchmarking, and survey research. 

This role also includes management of our Beta community of 1000+ members across multiple platforms, via Sharepoint, Facebook, and HockeyApp. As Beta PM, I regularly onboard new members and collect user attributes, set up e-mail campaigns, and recruit participants in the studies mentioned above.
